Available options for Lwt:

- GODI_LWT_SSL: Build support for ocaml-ssl in Lwt.
  Possible values: yes,no, <blank> = yes.

- GODI_LWT_GLIB: Build support for glib in Lwt.
  Possible values: yes,no, <blank> = yes.

- GODI_LWT_OCAMLTEXT: Build support for ocaml-text in Lwt.
  Possible values: yes,no, <blank> = yes.
